Use the standard library
This is how to solve of N:
   Remember that bits is []
   Remember that started is no

   Do this N times:
      When N is 0, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when

      Remember that q is quotient of N and 2
      Remember that r is remainder of N and 2

      When r is 1, then:
         Remember that started is yes
      End when

      When started is yes, then:
         When r is 0, then:
            Add bits to item 0 in "0"
         But, if not:
            Add bits to item 0 in "1"
         End when
      End when

      Remember that N is q
   End do

   Remember that answer is ""
   Remember that i is bits's length
   Do this bits's length times:
      Decrease i
      Add answer to item i in bits
   End do

   The answer is answer
Now you know